abstract: A poll has found that the percentage of registered voters in New York who agree with the protesters' views has risen since last week.
snippet: A poll has found that the percentage of registered voters in New York who agree with the protesters' views has risen since last week.
lead_paragraph: A Quinnipiac poll released Thursday found that 82 percent of New York voters are O.K. with the protests, and 58 percent agree with them. [Quinnipiac University]
